Name: Canning Rd & Stanhope Rd, Kalamunda
Description: It is very difficult to navigate safely from Stanhope Street onto Canning Road turning left or right as Canning Road is a very busy road.  This intersection is on a bend so you have very little view of cars coming from the south and have to move very quick once you deem it is safe to move onto Canning Rd. Looking left onto Canning Rd From Stanhope you can see clearly for quite a distance but not if you look right because of the bend. The cars are on top of you before you know it.
